ABOUT LAIKON DELI

Since 1976, Laikon Deli has been a Richmond favourite for gourmet foods, cheeses, cured meats and homemade specialities. From fresh meals, unique catering or bespoke functions, we bring the best of European flavour to your table.

Effortless entertaining, the Laikon way.

Whether you're planning a last-minute office lunch, a special celebration or a VIP event, Laikon Deli brings people together with delicious, no-fuss catering. Our thoughtfully curated boxes, platters and bites are made fresh daily, with dietary options available to suit every guest.
